-- John Lewis's Post-Christmas Sales Beat Its One-Day Record by More Than 30%
-- B y   B e n j a m i n   P u r v i s
-- 2010-12-30T10:54:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-30/john-lewis-s-post-christmas-sales-beat-its-one-day-record-by-more-than-30-.html
John Lewis said sales on Dec. 27 and
28 both beat the company’s previous record for a single day’s
sales, according to an e-mailed statement today.  It reported sales of 27.8 million pounds on Dec. 27, more
than 30 percent higher than the previous record day, which was
Dec. 27, 2008.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
